title: Handshake No Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone
description: Symbolizes agreement, a greeting, or the finalization of a deal between two individuals, using a medium skin tone. It signifies partnership and mutual understanding.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the handshake emoji showcases two hands meeting in a gesture of agreement or welcome, rendered with a warm, medium skin tone. Apple's signature glossy 3D shading imbues the hands with a realistic texture and soft rounded edges, suggesting a friendly and professional connection. This emoji on Apple devices beautifully conveys trust, collaboration, and a positive resolution to discussions.
